HEADWORD: Prostitutor
<hw>Pros"ti*tu`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.]</ety>
<def>One who prostitutes; one who submits himself, of or offers another,
to vile purposes.</def> <rj><au>Bp. Hurd.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
